  "description": "<p>Assistant Baker Needed – Singapore</p><p>We are looking for an Assistant Baker to join our bakery team in Singapore.</p><p>Candidates from Malaysia are welcome to apply.</p><p>Applicants with or without prior experience are encouraged to apply; training will be provided.</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Malaysian nationality</p><p>Ability to communicate in English and Chinese (mandatory)</p><p>Willingness to work in a fast-paced bakery environment</p><p>Physically fit and able to handle bakery duties</p><p>Responsible, punctual, and team-oriented</p><p>Salary:</p><p>SGD 2,000 – 2,300 per month (depending on experience)</p><p>Additional Details:</p><p>Full-time position</p><p>Working location: Singapore</p><p>Work permit provided (subject to eligibility)</p><p>Meals / overtime / rest days according to company policy</p><p>For enquiries or application, please contact:</p><p>+65 9361 2629</p>",
